quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  23,93,"Maaku: \"Jooma am si A hollii lam ko Й“e fodaa kon"
  23,94,"Jooma am, wata A waЙ—am e yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  23,95,"Pellet, Menen fii yo Men holle ko Men fodi Й“e kon ko Men HattanЙ“e [Й—um]"
  23,96,"DuГұir nden huunde Й“urnde moЖҙЖҙude [huunde] bonunde nden, ko Menen Anndi ko Й“e sifoto kon"
  23,97,"Maaku: \"Jooma, mi moolorii Ma immorde e kodooje Seytanuuji Й—in"
  23,98,Mi moolorii Ma Jooma am nde Й—i tawata lam
  23,99,"Haa si maayde arii e goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e nden, o wi'a: \"Jooma am ruttee lam"
  23,100,"Belajo'o men, mi gollay ko moЖҙЖҙi e nder kon ko mi accunoo, Й—um waЙ—ataa, ngol ko kanngol ko kanko wowli ngol, no hedde Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e heedo haa Г‘alnde nde Й“e imminoytee"
  23,101,"Si wuttaama ka alaadu, haray askaaji alah hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nden Г‘alnde, Й“e lanndandirtah"
  23,102,"Kala on mo jisti(teddi) manndake (peesirgal)muuЙ—um, haray ko Й“en Й—on woni maloyteeЙ“e Й“en"
  23,103,"Kala mo manndake [moЖҙЖҙi] muuЙ—um foygitii, (hoyi)haray ko Й“en Й—on woni hayruЙ“e pittaali muuЙ—um, ko ka nder Jahannama woni ko Й“e luttintee"
  23,104,"Yiite ngen no sunna geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hara kamЙ“e e nder magge ko Й“e ГұirЙ“iniiЙ“e"
  23,105,"Enee, hara Aayeeje Am Й—en laataaki no janngee e taweede mo'on, laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on fenna Й—e"
  23,106,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Joomi amen, ko malkiso amen ngon foolii men, men laatinoke yimЙ“e majjuЙ“e"
  23,107,"Joomi amen, yaltin men e magge, si men ruttike hara pellet, menen ko men tooГұuЙ“e"
  23,108,"O Daala: \"Г‘iiЙ“ee e nder magge wata on haalanam"
  23,109,"Pellet, laatinoke fedde e jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en hiЙ“e wi'a: \"Joomi amen, men gomЙ—inii haforan men YurmeЖҠaa men ko An Й“uri MoЖҙЖҙude YurmeteeЙ“e Й“en"
  23,110,"JogitiЙ—on Й“e jalnori(jalkigol), haa Й“e yejjintini on jaЕӢta Am, laatiЙ—on hiЙ—on jala Й“e"
  23,111,"Min Mi yoЙ“ii Й“e hannde sabu ko Й“e muГұГұinoo kon, pellet, kamЙ“e ko kamЙ“e woni malaaЙ“e Й“en"
  23,112,"O Daali: \"No foti heewde ko ГұiiЙ“uЙ—on ka leydi, limoore duuЙ“i"
  23,113,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Men ГұiiЙ“ii Гұallal maaЙ—um yoga e Гұallal, lanndo limooЙ“e Й“en"
  23,114,"O Daali: \"On ГұiiЙ“aali si wonaa seeЙ—a, sinndo onon on laatino hiЙ—on anndi"
  23,115,"Enee, on sikku wonndema ko Men Tagiri on ko puyndan, hara onon on ruttetaake faade ka Amen"
  23,116,"Alla Toowii LaamЙ—o GoonguЙ—o On, Rewetee- Й—o alah si wanaa Kanko Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin. @Corrected"
  23,117,"Kala nodduЙ—o wonndude e Alla reweteeЙ—o goo, daliil alanah mo e Й—um, anndu pellet, hasboo- re makko ko ka Joomi makko, pellet Kanko, O malnatah heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  23,118,"Maaku: \"Jooma am, Yaafo Yurmo ko An ЖҒuri MoЖҙЖҙude YurmeteeЙ“e Й“en"